00:02:54.460 --> 00:02:55.780
The message was sent

00:02:55.780 --> 00:02:56.860
at exactly 1:30 PM.

00:02:57.260 --> 00:02:58.060
To the second.

00:02:58.660 --> 00:02:59.620
So I think

00:02:59.780 --> 00:03:01.500
it's very likely a scheduled message.

00:03:05.220 --> 00:03:06.780
Do you think he was gambling?

00:03:08.060 --> 00:03:10.060
